The MD5000 series controllers use a virtual serial port via the USB interface. It requires to install the USB driver before using. You can also install the MD51_52OPTOOL to set some parameters that can not be changed in Micro-Manager (such as: customized acceleration time, motor current, sensor setting, home search setting, etc.).

To download the MD5000 USB driver and software, please follow this link:
http://www.novaelec.co.jp/down/soft/md515230ds.zip

To download the MD5000 user manual, please follow this link:
http://www.novaelec.co.jp/eng/down/file/md515230de.pdf

The MD5000 series Serial port settings are as following:

